{"tid":2492984,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【bitcoin】土耳其禁虛擬貨幣交易　比特幣以太幣跌逾3%、狗狗幣逆市升","createTime":"2021-04-17T13:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T14:13:36.000Z","uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"082362d7b2bafa490bb10d9f1b933ce60a852cc6","tid":2492984,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:49:54.000Z","msg":"土耳其央行宣布，由於虛擬貨幣缺乏中央監管，而且暫未有數碼資產的監管機制，因此自4月30日起禁止使用虛擬貨幣直接或間接購買商品或服務，消息衝擊加密貨幣市場，比特幣（bitcoin）由高位回落，曾跌逾4%，低見60033美元；以太幣亦跌逾3%，低見2328美元。<br />\n<br />\n不過，狗狗幣（Dogecoin）升勢持續，過去24小時升逾2倍，高見0.45美元。<br />\n<br />\n土耳其指，虛擬貨幣的市值相當波動，數碼錢包可以被盜用，或進行非法事宜，而且有關交易不能撤銷。土耳其上周曾要求調查虛擬貨幣的持有情況，如今禁止透過虛擬貨幣進行交易，但有關規定未提及存款部分。<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2934285/%E3%80%90bitcoin%E3%80%91%E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6%E7%A6%81%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E3%80%80%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%A3%E8%B7%8C%E9%80%BE3-%E3%80%81%E7%8B%97%E7%8B%97%E5%B9%A3%E9%80%86%E5%B8%82%E5%8D%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2934285%2F%25E3%2580%2590bitcoin%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%259C%259F%25E8%2580%25B3%25E5%2585%25B6%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%2599%259B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%25AF%2594%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E8%25B7%258C%25E9%2580%25BE3-%25E3%2580%2581%25E7%258B%2597%25E7%258B%2597%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E9%2580%2586%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%258D%2587&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=9f77d371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2934285/%E3%80%90bitcoin%E3%80%91%E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6%E7%A6%81%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E3%80%80%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%A3%E8%B7%8C%E9%80%BE3-%E3%80%81%E7%8B%97%E7%8B%97%E5%B9%A3%E9%80%86%E5%B8%82%E5%8D%87</a>"},{"pid":"4725f9f7e718fc834e287a8e365af9fab71597e7","tid":2492984,"uid